{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ac8ae12f-d4fa-4160-88ea-e9194e6852eb", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac8ae12f-d4fa-4160-88ea-e9194e6852eb@5.pkg/1772597647371/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597647814", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac8ae12f-d4fa-4160-88ea-e9194e6852eb@5.pkg/1772597647371/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597647814"}, "identifier": "ac8ae12f-d4fa-4160-88ea-e9194e6852eb", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>承担责任需要付出代价，如时间、精力，做的不好会受到他人埋怨，因此本题中①②③符合题意。④选项说明承担责任会收到回报，不符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列属于承担责任时付出代价的有(　　)</p>\n\n<p>①小刚常年帮助孤寡老人，因此失去了很多娱乐时间</p>\n\n<p>②校运动会接力比赛中小明因失误受到同学埋怨</p>\n\n<p>③小强为了办板报而错过去公园游玩的机会</p>\n\n<p>④小云获得全校演讲比赛冠军，同学对她表示祝贺</p>\n", "title": "下列属于承担责任时付出代价的有(　　)①小刚常年帮助孤寡老人，因此失去了很多娱乐时间②校运动会接力比赛中小明因失误受到同学埋怨③小强为了办板报而错过去公园游玩的机会④小云获得全校演讲比赛冠军，同学对她表示祝贺", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac8ae12f-d4fa-4160-88ea-e9194e6852eb@5.pkg/item.json?v=1754665811580", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE